    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/18cbf70b7e30579bf0ab4c78969ba967.avif?t=1769194358\" width=612 height=163 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/a67011037801c60876b59cac61e4c596.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ 探索脚下不断变化的程序化土地。 <br>🗡️ 在凶猛的蛮族部落面前生存下来。 <br>🎆 发掘深层系统和强大的连击。 <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/d29bf6e655bb765b147af772c5982c18.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 混合超过200种改变游戏规则的技术。 <br>🎲 即兴应变，充分利用每一次独特的冒险。 <br>❄️ 看着你的选择雪球般滚动，创造出截然不同的文明。 <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/a67011037801c60876b59cac61e4c596.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎴 构建完美的卡组，制定独特的策略。 <br>🔨 在每个时代升级你的卡牌、单位和城市。 <br>📈 建立一个经得起时间考验的帝国，从石器时代到奇点时代。 <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/fa6615097a0d01eb922e798f634df8eb.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 完成艰难挑战，解锁新内容。 <br>✨ 在比赛之间获得永久升级。 <br>⚰️ 以壮观的方式失败，然后再次挑战！ <br> </p>",
